gobblin.aws

Class GobblinAWSTaskRunner

  • java.lang.Object
    • gobblin.cluster.GobblinTaskRunner
      • gobblin.aws.GobblinAWSTaskRunner

  • @Alpha
public class GobblinAWSTaskRunner
extends GobblinTaskRunner
    Class running on worker nodes managing services for executing Gobblin WorkUnits.

    This class makes use of super class GobblinTaskRunner to run: 1. GobblinHelixTaskFactory for creating GobblinHelixTasks that Helix manages to run Gobblin data ingestion tasks. 2. HelixManager to work with Helix and act as Helix participant to execute tasks. More AWS specific services can be added in future to this class that are required to be run on Gobblin cluster worker.

    Note: Shutdown initiated by GobblinClusterManager via a Helix message of subtype HelixMessageSubTypes.WORK_UNIT_RUNNER_SHUTDOWN is handled by super class GobblinTaskRunner
